Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:13.67,Narration,Narration,0,0,0,,{What he saw had lulled him into a trance.}Những gì trước mắt đã đưa cậu ta \Nvào trạng thái bị thôi miên.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:18.18,Narration,Narration,0,0,0,,{The bra he had failed to steal\Nwas hanging from the wall.}Áo vú cậu ta trộm hụt được treo trên tường.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:21.18,Narration,Narration,0,0,0,,{He could sense that it was a trap.}Chắc chắn đó là bẫy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:26.04,Narration,Narration,0,0,0,,{But at the same time, adolescent\Nfantasies were stirring in his mind.}Nhưng cùng lúc, trí tưởng tượng tuổi mới lớn trỗi dậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.93,0:01:31.06,Narration,Narration,0,0,0,,{If the woman this bra had\Nbelonged to was responsible...}Nếu chủ nhân của cái áo vú này cố tình làm nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:37.20,Narration,Narration,0,0,0,,{Could she be waiting on the other side\Nof the window, with no bra on at all?}Tức là chị ta đang ở bên\N kia bức tường không mặc áo vú.
