Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:46.41,DefaultItalicsTop,Eita,0,0,0,,{This must be a room in \Nthat run-down building...}Đây là căn phòng nào đó ở chung cư...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:50.88,DefaultItalicsTop,Eita,0,0,0,,{The question is who it belongs to.}Vấn đề là phòng của ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:53.59,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Hurry and put it on me.}Nhanh mặc nó vào cho chị đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:06.76,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{Excuse me? Did you just sigh?}Này, thở dài cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:10.04,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{I was nice enough to bring you\Ninside after I saw you out cold}Ta đã rất tử tế khi thấy nhóc bất tỉnh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.52,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{with that bra in your hands!}với cái áo vú trên tay đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.88,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{Okay, you just clicked your tongue at me!}Giờ lại còn tặc lưỡi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.52,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{I know you're the underwear thief, y'know!}Ta biết nhóc là kẻ trộm đồ lót rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:22.80,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{I'm remaining silent.\NI want legal defense present.}Tôi sẽ giữ im lặng, hãy đưa luật sư đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:25.35,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Until then, I'm not saying another word.}Cho đến khi đó tôi sẽ không nói gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:30.34,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{What, did they teach you\Nabout that at school yesterday?}Gì chứ? Hôm qua mới được học trên trường à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:32.45,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Better not sit up yet.}Đừng ngồi dậy vội.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:36.02,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{You might've hit your head when you fell.}Vì cậu bị té đập đầu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:40.34,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Why'd you collapse? Does that happen often?}Sao lại bất tỉnh? Chuyện hay xảy ra à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:45.05,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{No... I remember there was this pain\Nin my left shoulder, and then I passed out.}Không... tôi nhớ là tự nhiên\Nthấy đau vai trái và sau đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:47.19,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Sounds like anemia.}Thiếu máu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:51.31,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I may or may not have heard something\Nabout pickled eggplant being good for that.}Tôi cảm giác như từng nghe ai nói\Ncà tím ngâm có tác dụng bổ sung sắt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.18,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Eat.}Ăn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.22,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{That sounds made-up.}Nghe mông lung vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:01.09,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{I don't really like pickled foods.\NEspecially eggplant.}Tôi không thích đồ ngâm, đặc biệt là cà tím.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:02.07,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I hear you.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:06.60,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Ever since I tried the stuff Ono-san's mom\Nsends him, I don't like it anymore, either.}Ngay cả tôi cũng chán lắm rồi\N khi phải ăn đồ mẹ anh Ono gửi đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:09.20,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{Come on, Kuro-kun, that's just rude!}Này Kuro, thất lễ quá đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.42,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Anyone home?}Có ai ở nhà hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.91,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Hey, you're drinking!}Đang uống à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.96,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{I want in!}Tôi vào với.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.64,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Oh, right.}À phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:21.11,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Here, Ono-san. I got you \Na beer, so now we're even!}Đây, bia của ông đây. Tha cho tôi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:27.22,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{Er, you actually drank more than one, but...}À thực ra... cô uống nhiều hơn 1 lon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.64,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Aw, quit whining!}Đừng lèm bèm nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.18,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{So, what's with the kid?}Thằng nhóc nào đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:34.20,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{W-Well... He's...}À thì nó...
