Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:45.24,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{You did?! Well, thanks!}Thế à? Cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:47.63,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{It's fine...}Không có gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:50.26,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Ooh, pickled eggplant!}A, cà tím ngâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.45,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Hey, kid.}Này nhóc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.66,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{You don't want the bra anymore?}Không muốn áo vú nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.96,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Uh, no.}Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:03.96,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{I think I'm okay now.\NConsidering I almost became a criminal...}Tôi ổn. So với việc gần như thành tội phạm.
