Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:16.73,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{At Kodan High.}Cao trung Kodan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:20.48,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Seriously? You're that old?}Đùa à? Cấp 3 á?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:24.11,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{You ought to know better, then.\NMaybe I should call the cops.}Thôi, quả nhiên tôi nên gọi cảnh sát.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:28.00,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Wait! Please don't! I'll do anything!}Khoan đã! Tôi sẽ làm mọi thứ! Đừng gọi!
