Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:28.32,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Drone guy! Hey, drone guy!}Anh drone! Anh drone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:34.10,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{Seriously, why do you call... me... that?}Lại nữa! Đã bảo là đừng gọi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:35.58,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Gimme that drone!}Cho em mượn drone đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.08,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Come on, the drone!}Nào, drone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:45.48,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{It's flying! It really flies!}Nó đang bay! Đang bay kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.09,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{I'll let you go next!}Tí nữa em sẽ cho anh mượn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.79,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Do you know how to use it?}Anh biết cách xài không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:52.97,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{I've flown a few suicide drones before.}Trước đây tôi từng lái vài \Ncon drone ném bom tự sát.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:56.95,FlashbackItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{The blond foreigner in a \Nblue hoodie and glasses...}Ngoại quốc tóc vàng áo Hoodie xanh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.80,FlashbackItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{I gotta call Kuro-san.}Phải gọi Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:02.60,FlashbackItalics,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{Just when I thought it\Nhad quieted down some...}Gần đây có vẻ yên tĩnh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.74,FlashbackItalics,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{There's that drone again.}Lại là con drone đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:06.35,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Yoshida-sensei.}Thầy Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:07.73,Flashback,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{Oh, right, right.}À rồi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:12.41,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Thank you so much for letting \Nme see your manuscript.}Cảm ơn vì đã cho tôi xem qua thứ này.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:16.99,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Your depiction of the grief these ninja go\Nthrough was so vivid. I was honestly touched.}Sự miêu tả về nỗi đau mà những ninja này \Ntrải qua thật sống động. Tôi rất cảm động
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:18.95,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Excellent work!}Thật tuyệt vời!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.98,Flashback,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{I'm glad to hear that. It's quite a relief.}Vậy thì tốt, tôi yên tâm rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:26.46,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{This scene where the ninja \Nare all wiped out, especially,}Đặc biệt là cảnh ninja bị thổi bay này.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.47,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{had me holding my sides in laughter.}Khiến tôi phải cười đau cả bụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.63,Flashback,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{Uh, that's supposed to be a tragic scene...}Ủa? Cảnh đó là cảnh buồn mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.64,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Now, I'd like to talk to you about\Na few edits I was thinking of.}Giờ thì tôi muốn một vài điều chỉnh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.64,Flashback,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{R-Right.}À vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.55,Flashback,Hibi,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:44.39,Flashback,Hibi,0,0,0,,{Crossing up upon the bypass,\Nheading to paradise in first class!}Vượt qua đường tránh, tiến tới\N thiên đường trên khoang hạng nhất!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:47.09,Flashback,Hibi,0,0,0,,{With an eye looking on the\Nfuture, and even the past!}Với ánh mắt nhìn về tương lai và quá khứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:48.15,Flashback,Hibi,0,0,0,,{And then...}Sau đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.15,Flashback,Taira,0,0,0,,{Shut the fuck up and walk, baldo.}Im mồm và bước nhanh lên thằng hói.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.65,Flashback,Hibi,0,0,0,,{Oh, sure.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:54.83,FlashbackItalics,Hibi,0,0,0,,{That's my master for you.}Đó là sư phụ của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:58.78,FlashbackItalics,Hibi,0,0,0,,{He's bald himself, but he calls me,\Nwith my long hair, baldo.}Luôn xấu mồm, ổng bị \Nhói nhưng cứ hay gọi mình hói.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:04.16,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{First, I'd cut this part. It's just repeating\Nwhat was on the previous page.}Đầu tiên là phần này không cần thiết. \NNó chỉ nhắc lại phần trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:06.62,Flashback,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{B-But that's...}N-Nhưng đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:09.17,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Cơ mà hãy xoá bỏ chương này luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:12.99,Flashback,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{Wh-Whoa, that's basically\Na rewrite at that point!}K-Khoan đã! Vậy là viết lại gần hết còn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:15.30,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Oh, this can go, too.}A, chỗ này cũng không cần.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:19.93,FlashbackTop,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{And this scene at the beginning...\NI'd like you to rewrite that.}Và cảnh ban đầu... ngài hãy viết lại luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.90,Flashback,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{What happened to all that praise?}Lúc nãy mới khen mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:24.18,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Oh, sorry, the office is calling.}A, văn phòng gọi tôi.
