Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:31.57,Signs,Phone sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H7C807C&\b0\fs10\an7\bord2\3c&HF0F2F2&\fscy120\fax-.1\fay.01\frz352.5\frx6\fry356\move(338,218,338,180)}{Understood}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:31.57,FlashbackTop,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Sensei, a question...}Tiên sinh, tôi có câu hỏi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.57,Signs,Phone sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H7C807C&\b0\fs10\an7\bord2\3c&HF0F2F2&\fscy120\fax-.1\fay.01\frz352.5\frx6\fry356\move(326,266,326,234)}{Roger that}
