Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:36.07,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{What's the name of this slu—\NI mean, apartment building?}Tên của khu rách nát--, căn hộ này là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.95,Flashback,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{It's Murayama Flats.}Nhà thuê Murayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.95,Signs,Zoom in,0,0,0,,{\c&H535452&\b0\fs18\an1\bord3\3c&HF0F2F2&\pos(246,124)}{Capture the foreigner.\N2-X-X Nishiki-cho in Nerima City.\NMurayama Flats.}Nhà thuê Murayama\N Nishiki, thành phố Nerima
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:45.46,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Sorry, my boss has urgent business for me.}Xin lỗi, có vẻ sếp cần gặp tôi gấp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:48.48,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Please have the corrections ready\Nbefore 3:00 PM tomorrow.}Xin hãy chỉnh sửa lại trước 15h ngày mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:51.30,Flashback,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{W-W-Wait! There's no way!}Hả? K-K-Không thể đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.78,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{If you'll excuse me.}Vậy tôi xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:57.01,Flashback,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{W-Wait...}K-Khoan đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:05.23,FlashbackItalics,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Yoshida-sensei.}Tiên sinh Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:08.44,FlashbackItalics,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{He's so anxious and hunched over.}Hẳn đang rất lo lắng và bấn loạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:12.08,FlashbackItalics,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{He'll probably be up all night\Nwith those corrections.}Đêm nay tiên sinh sẽ thức trắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:16.24,FlashbackItalics,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Good luck. I'll see you again tomorrow.}Chúc may mắn, ngày mai tôi sẽ đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:19.24,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H3A4B79&\pos(294,70)}{Cigarettes}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.24,Flashback,Taira,0,0,0,,{Pops, gimme some smokes and matches.}Ông chú, thuốc lá và diêm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:23.24,Flashback,Owner,0,0,0,,{Store's not even open anymore.\NYou should head on out of here.}Cửa hàng đóng rồi, kiếm chỗ khác đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:25.92,Flashback,Taira,0,0,0,,{Don't be like that! Help a guy out.}Đừng thế mà! Bán cho tôi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:30.01,Flashback,Owner,0,0,0,,{Who the hell gets their orders from\Ncolor-coded matches in this day and age?}Giờ này ai mà mua thuốc \Nlá theo mã màu như ông nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:34.38,Flashback,Owner,0,0,0,,{These days, there's those Marishitens\Nand that Escape thing...}Thời nay là Marishiten và cái thứ Escape gì đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:37.88,Flashback,Owner,0,0,0,,{A buncha fancy gizmos with \Nold-fashioned names stuck on 'em.}Một đống thứ độc dị phong cách\N cũ và dán đầy tên lên đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:40.69,Flashback,Owner,0,0,0,,{Which leaves guys like us\Ntreated like antiques!}Nó khiến chúng ta cứ như những kẻ đi sau thời đại.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:44.51,Flashback,Taira,0,0,0,,{I happen to like antiques, myself.}Tôi thì thích những thứ xưa cũ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:48.14,Flashback,Taira,0,0,0,,{The thing about tech is you can't\Nrely on it in the heat of the moment,}Công nghệ cao sẽ không giúp\N được gì ở những thời điểm quyết định.,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:50.02,Flashback,Taira,0,0,0,,{when your life is on the line.}như khi mạng sống bị đe doạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:54.07,Flashback,Hibi,0,0,0,,{I hear the cheers, they come at me for years!}Tôi nghe thấy tiếng hò reo, hãy đến đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.65,Flashback,Taira,0,0,0,,{Come on, Hibi, let's go.}Đi thôi Hibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.65,Flashback,Hibi,0,0,0,,{Where to?}Đi đâu ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:01.41,Flashback,Taira,0,0,0,,{Time for your first mission\Nat Murayama Flats.}Nhiệm vụ đầu tiên ở chung cư Murayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.16,Flashback,Taira,0,0,0,,Tất cả kẻ ở đó là kẻ thù.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:08.16,Flashback,Hibi,0,0,0,,{Hell yeah. Finally some combat.}Ngon lành, cuối cùng cũng được thực chiến.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:16.17,FlashbackItalics,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{The target is on the shared balcony\Non the second floor...}Mục tiêu... trên ban công chung tầng 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:28.68,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Hey, let me see it already!}Này, trả cho cháu đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:38.36,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Pardon me!}Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.20,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Ow...}Đau...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.83,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Hey! What the heck was that?}Này! Chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.94,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{You okay? Any injuries?}Ổn chứ? Có bị thương không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:52.46,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Yeah! I skinned my knee!}Có! Đầu gối trầy hết nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:56.29,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Sorry about that. But civilian\Ncasualties come with the job.}Xin lỗi nhé. Nhưng thường dân bị \Nthương là không thể tránh khỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:58.42,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{If you want to file a complaint,}Nếu muốn phàn nàn,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:01.21,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{submit it to the local\Ncourthouse within 30 days.}hãy gửi đơn đến toà án địa\N phương trong vòng 30 ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:03.72,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Not that it'll matter.}Cơ mà chắc cũng chẳng ai quan tâm đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:07.43,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{You're a high schooler, so you ought\Nto understand what's going on.}Là học sinh cấp 3 chắc cũng hiểu tình hình nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:10.34,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{If you want to avoid trouble,\Nkeep that mouth zipped.}Nếu muốn yên ổn thì đừng hé mồm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:12.98,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{I-I won't say a word!}E-Em xin thề.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:16.73,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{That drone of yours has\Nreally complicated things.}Cái drone đó đúng là phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:19.97,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{And I had an appointment\Nat the beautician later...}Tí nữa có hẹn với tiệm làm đẹp...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:21.22,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Now I'm gonna be late.}Giờ thì không kịp rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:25.87,Flashback,Eita,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sorry, but... I also\Nhave no idea what's going on.}E-Em xin lỗi nhưng chị có nói thế thì cũng...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:32.62,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{Well, I'll still win in the end.}Kệ đi, cuối cùng mình cũng thắng thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:49.54,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{She vanished?!}Biến mất?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:51.48,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Damn it!}Chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:30.18,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{He's had electrocution conditioning.}Hắn đã bị điện giật mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.01,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{I screwed up.}Mình tính sai rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:36.10,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Was there bulletproof gel in her shirt?}Áo chống đạn sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:41.80,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Is that enough to block .22 LR rounds?}Nó đủ cản khẩu .22 LR này không?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:48.20,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{If hitting his heart with the taser won't\Nwork, I'll have to aim for his head.}Nếu bắn vào tim không ảnh hưởng\N thì mình sẽ nhắm vào đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:53.70,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{I'll intercept his shot with my hand and\Nthen redirect it to avoid a critical wound.}Mình sẽ dùng tay để chuyển hướng viên đạn \Nđến vùng chấn thương không nghiêm trọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:56.58,Flashback,Suzuki,0,0,0,,{I am not dying here.}Mình sẽ không chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:22:00.21,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Her movements... She's not begging for mercy.}Cách di chuyển đó... \Ncô ta không định cầu xin tha thứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:03.84,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Are ninja that fixated on survival?}Ninja nào cũng như vậy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:10.35,Flashback,Hibi,0,0,0,,{Yo, yo, is someone playing with my yo-yo?}Yo yo, có ai chơi với ta không, yo yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:14.35,Flashback,Hibi,0,0,0,,{Damn, you both look like shit.}Này, cả hai trông tàn tạ thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:17.48,Flashback,Hibi,0,0,0,,{You pick a fight with the wrong person?}Chiến nhầm người rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.66,Flashback,Hibi,0,0,0,,{Well, the star's here now.\NSo where's my applause?}Ngôi sao đã đến, còn không vỗ tay?
